                     Release Notes for SAMRAI v4.1.2

     (notes for previous releases may be found in /SAMRAI/docs/release)

*****************************************************************************

Please direct any questions related to these notes to the SAMRAI development
team by sending email to samrai@llnl.gov.

*****************************************************************************

VERSION 4.1.2

Version 4.1.2 is a minor release update.  Please also see the release notes
for versions 4.1.0 and 4.1.1 located in subdirectory docs/release

*****************************************************************************

Where to report Bugs
--------------------

If a bug is found in the SAMRAI library, we ask that you kindly report
it to us so that we may fix it.

Please send email to samrai-bugs@llnl.gov or post an issue on github.
https://github.com/LLNL/SAMRAI



*****************************************************************************

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                Significant bug fixes
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

*****************************************************************************



----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                Summary of what's new
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                Summary of what's changed
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

1) The recommended versions of Umpire and RAJA have been updated, and
there are minor code changes within SAMRAI to keep things compatible with
these libraries.

*****************************************************************************

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                Details about what's new
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

1) When building with the new versions of RAJA and Umpire, C++ 14 is required.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                Details about what's changed
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

1) The recommended versions of Umpire and RAJA to be used with SAMRAI are now
Umpire v. 2022.03.1 and RAJA v. 2022.03.0.  Some minor changes to SAMRAI are
included in this release to maintain compatibility with these libraries.
There are no changes to the SAMRAI API.

This SAMRAI release is not expected to be backward compatible with earlier
releases of Umpire and RAJA.

=============================================================================
=============================================================================
